    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start, but my students really need to go deeper for a high-level tournament. Could you expand on those first two points? Specifically, can you provide a more detailed, philosophically rigorous breakdown of the \"state sovereignty\" argument and the \"rule of law\" argument? They need to be able to defend these points against accusations that they are just being \"unwelcoming.\" They need the actual academic/legal reasoning behind them.",
